title: Full-Length Genome Sequence of a Variant Porcine Epidemic Diarrhea Virus Strain, CH/GDZQ/2014, Responsible for a Severe Outbreak of Diarrhea in Piglets in Guangdong, China, 2014
body: The complete genome sequence of PEDV strain CH/GDZQ/2014 was deposited in GenBank under the accession number KM242131.
